The star has been working hard and looking super slim, leading to many of her followers asking how she managed to do it.Taking to Instagram on Monday, Zahara revealed that her change came from both patience and perseverance. "A huge part of losing weight is believing you can do it and realizing its not going to happen overnight," Zahara told her fans.To emphasises the point she posted a picture of herself before and after her weight loss journey.A photo posted by Bulelwa Mkutukana (@zaharasa) on Oct 31, 2016 at 2:24am PDTA photo posted by Bulelwa Mkutukana (@zaharasa) on Oct 31, 2016 at 2:24am PDTSpeaking to TshisaLIVE back in June, Zahara explained that her weight loss journey began when she looked in the mirror, and did not like what she saw. "I looked at myself in the mirror and thought, 'girl you are not even 30 yet and you are wearing Spanx under your dresses. I was just depressed and uninspired at the time," Zahara said.Since then, Zahara has worked hard to change both her body and her style, including a decision a few weeks ago to cut her trademark locks for something a little shorter.A photo posted by Bulelwa Mkutukana (@zaharasa) on Oct 24, 2016 at 9:53am PDT A photo posted by Bulelwa Mkutukana (@zaharasa) on Oct 24, 2016 at 9:53am PDT Find the hottest celebrity and entertainment news on TshisaLIVE or follow TshisaLIVE on Facebook and Twitter.